title: All-Time Coffee Co.
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee shop opened in 2015 by a couple of whom one is vegan. Menu offers a vegan version of each dish using imitation meat and vegan cheese. Has Bonsoy, almond, and coconut milk for drinks; vegan marshmallow upon request; several varieties of vegan donuts. Chocolate used in drinks are vegan. Decor is modern fit with New York loft feel. Has Wi-Fi.
